{"tid":793182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"放迷你倉30萬cash唔見咗？ 失魂婆婆惹爆竊驚魂","createTime":"2018-08-25T07:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-25T09:11:45.000Z","uid":122,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81e438c7bf4004d431d67f68ac3f1d2cf3acf889","tid":793182,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:32:28.000Z","msg":"早上9時半許，警方接報旺角廣東道1123號一間迷你倉發生懷疑爆竊案，涉款30萬元。警員到場接觸到報案女子，據她所講，她受一名老婦朋友所託，今早到老婦所租用的迷你倉內，拿取存放在倉內的30萬元現金，但她遍尋不獲，懷疑迷你倉曾遭人爆竊，於是報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n不過，警員到場調查後，並未發現現場有曾遭爆竊痕迹，於是致電老婦協助調查，老婦始記起該30萬元現金其實存放在其他地方，證實為誤會一場。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff394bb41cd4f569267023d9c12c6119e5cdb47","tid":793182,"uid":176166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a59e82f7ffd4e3004f60052f5e0a0d2cb4d9cebf","tid":793182,"uid":67028,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"廢老傑出系列"},{"pid":"8c5e2720057705824959cbe3f3d08c056c69a8db","tid":793182,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T07:33:33.000Z","msg":"現金擺迷你倉"},{"pid":"58fe2334983f4487e0c5f2b1777d929e8dd0f47a","tid":793182,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:06:03.000Z","msg":"浪費驚力"},{"pid":"7cbc920fb629315d974b188de1916ba671de4fd4","tid":793182,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:28:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19d45a27c99946438fb4272cf55294bc093cff09","tid":793182,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"明明放佐15萬係藍鑵曲奇， 放佐15萬係美心月餅盒， 咁快又唔記得&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0b6e3f5d6444ff7b2afbaa51810b5aa2548aeaad","tid":793182,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7cbc920fb629315d974b188de1916ba671de4fd4","tid":793182,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25